[Extendicare is a rehabilitation facility with 78 private and 30 semi-private rooms for long-term care residents and 32 private skilled nursing beds located in Dothan, Alabama (https://www.extendicarehealth.com/rehabilitation/). Dothan, with a population of 65 496 at the 2010 census, is near the state's southeastern corner, approximately 20 miles (32 km) west of the Georgia state line and 16 miles (26 km) north of Florida state line (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dothan,_Alabama). A map showing the location of Dothan can be found at https://www.google.com/maps/place/Dothan,+AL. Dothan is the county seat of Houston County, which is adjacent to Henry and Geneva counties. A map of Alabama counties can be found at https://geology.com/county-map/alabama.shtml. - Mod.ML]

